ree zones of low sulfidation gold occurrences in altered volcanic rocks covering a strike length of over five kilometres km these results confirm the trebol propertys potential to host at or near surface shallow dipping gold mineralization that could potentially be mined with very low strip ratiosmineralization throughout the trebol area is characterized by shallow to moderately dipping tabular shaped vein and hydrothermal breccia zones within andesite outcropping horizons of the siliceous material have yielded impressive gold values in the trenching see bgold press release dated november   and the drilling has shown that many of these zones extend up to  metres down dip and show continuity over distances of several hundreds of metres of strike length due to the shallow dips associated with the gold mineralization most of mineralization is near surface and mostly oxidizedthe three zones drilled to date are cerro domingo the paola zone and the trebol north zone drill holes contain up to  grams per tonne gt gold over  metres in hole tr drilling by radius gold in  first located the cerro domingo zone and this has been confirmed and expanded in the recent drilling the  drilling campaign cut mineralization in the cerro domingo paola and trebol north zones with drill holes containing up to  gt gold over  metres in hole tr in the cerro domingo zone up to  gt gold over  metres in hole tr in the paola zone and up to  gt gold over  metres in hole tr in the trebol north zone drill intervals are highlighted below bgold drill holes gold from to interval gold gt cappedzone drill hole metres metres metres gt at  gtcerro domingo tr      including      tr      including      and      tr      including      tr      itr      including      tr      tr      tr     paola zone tr      tr      including      tr      including      tr      tr      tr      tr      iitr      and     trebol north itr      including     i indicates some intervals may have had poor recoveriesiiresassay pending due to low standard failureprevious radius gold drill holes gold from to interval gold gt cappedzone drill hole metres metres metres gt at  gtcerro domingo itrdh      trdh      and      including      trdh      and      trdha      trdh      trdh     i indicates some intervals may have had poor recoveriesthe  drill campaign at trebol has successfully identified several areas that will require additional drilling to define the extent of the mineralization the mineralization remains open to the north and south and in the covered areas between the three zones in addition the companys geologists continue to discover more low sulfidation epithermal gold outcrop and float occurrences within the concession that contain plus  gt gold assays in grab and chip samples over  km of the  km total strike length of the trend in addition a parallel zone has been located three km east of cerro domingo where preliminary grab sampling of similar siliceous material has yielded values up to  gt goldexploration is ongoing at trebol and will continue as bgold geologists compile the recent drill data and plan the next round of trenching and drillingsamples for trebol are submitted with blanks and industry certified standards inserted in the field and prior to reception at inspectorates prep lab in managua pulps are then analyzed at inspectorates labs in reno nevada check assays are currently being selected now that the drilling program has been completed and will be sent to als labs in vancouver canada except where noted all results stated in this announcement have passed bgolds quality assurance and quality control qaqc protocolsthe exploration programs for the company are reviewed and the results approved by tom garagan bgolds qualified person under national instrument on behalf of bgold corptom garagan senior vice president of explorationon behalf of radius gold incsimon ridgway president and chief executive officerfor more information on bgold please visit the company web site at wwwbgoldcomfor more information on radius gold please visit the radius golds web site at wwwradiusgoldcomthe securities described herein have not been and will not be registered under the united states securities act of  as amended and may not be offered or sold in the united states absent registration or an applicable exemption from registration requirementssome of the statements contained in this release are forwardlooking statements such as estimates and statements that describe the companys future plans objectives or goals including words to the effect that the company or management expects a stated condition or result to occur since forwardlooking statements address future events and conditions by their very nature they involve inherent risks and uncertainties actual results in each case could differ materially from those currently anticipated in such statementsreblogsharetweetsharepopular in the communitytexas deputy facing charges in deadly altercation at dennys restaurant terminated reactionsamazing images of light under desert archways reactionsteenage cheerleader accused of killing newborn baby and burying it in garden reactionstrump in angry twitter spree declares ‘the complete power to pardon’ reactionspowerful earthquake hits greece and turkey reactionsanthony scaramucci deletes old tweets criticizing trump reactionsluis fonsi on justin biebers spanish despacito hitting no  reactionssaturday night live honours sean spicer in hilarious melissa mccarthy tribute to outgoing press secretary reactionsjohn heard dies ‘home alone’ actor was  reactionscarrie underwood shows off her killer body in a no filter bikini instagram reactionsmarch for australian justine damond shot dead by minneapolis police reactionssevere storms on the move in the midwest reactionshistoric pearl river mart reopens to bring crosscultural joy to nyc reactionskey witness identified in minneapolis officerinvolved shooting that killed bridetobe reactionsmom encourages parents to teach their child